Implementation:
* Viewports (with lists of objects to be rendered) - only one viewport is supported now
* Option to reload the UI init file


Data:
* Data source
 - basic model format
 - Text loader


Layout:
* Anchors


Implement other UI components:
* Checkbox
* Scrollable field for displaying text and log output
* Slider
* Arrows and lines
* Images


When layout engine and ui components have been implemented,
begin implementation of basic dialogs (in lua):
* LoadObjectFile
* FileEditor


Visual:
